Tower of Dexterity									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																			DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Whenever you use your Harrow casting ability, for each card you draw from the suit of Dexterity, you gain a +1 bonus on Reflex saves and to AC until the beginning of your next turn.																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.277
